subject:

A CHRISTIAN SHOULD BE
===================================================================
verse:
Let this mind be in you, which was also in Christ Jesus.
Philippians 2:5 (AI)

===================================================================
reflection:

The Answer: A mind through which Christ thinks. A voice
through which Christ speaks. A heart through which Christ
loves. A hand through which Christ helps. How is Christ
using you?

===================================================================
prayer:

Lord Jesus, think Your thoughts through my mind, speak Your
truth through my voice, love through my heart, and serve
through my hands. Conform me to Your likeness so that in
word and deed I become a living witness of Your grace. Use
me today as Your vessel for the good of others and the glory
of Your name. Amen. (AI)

===================================================================
body_text:

